INSERT INTO scioly_user_stats (
            discord_user_id,
            phpbb_user_id,
            username,
            forums_avatar,
            forums_post_count,
            forums_thanks_received,
            forums_thanks_given,
            wiki_edit_count,
            test_ex_upload_count,
            gallery_score,
            gallery_post_count) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
            ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE
            discord_user_id = ?,
            phpbb_user_id = ?,
            username = ?,
            forums_avatar = ?,
            forums_post_count = ?,
            forums_thanks_received = ?,
            forums_thanks_given = ?,
            wiki_edit_count = ?,
            test_ex_upload_count = ?,
            gallery_score = ?,
            gallery_post_count = ?
